bioghist.p:
Ardath Walter Burks was born May 1, 1915 in Covington, Kentucky to Alonzo Edwin Burks, an assistant freight agent 
		for the C  O Railroad, and Clara Grace McCracken Burks.  He married Virginia Jane Lyle Burks on November 15, 1941; 
		their son, Stephen Riki Burks, was born in 1954.

